load_file()` 和 `download_file()`\n41:   - 测试未初始化 `session_id` 时抛出 `ValueError`\n42:   - 测试正常上传返回 parsed JSON\n43:   - 测试正常下载返回 bytes\n44:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_code_interpreter.py`\n45:   - Verify: session 验证和文件操作正确\n46: \n47: - [ ] **T1.6** 测试 `close()` 方法\n48:   - 测试关闭 `dp_client` 和 `cp_client`\n49:   - 测试有 `session_id` 时删除 session\n50:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_code_interpreter.py`\n51:   - Verify: 资源清理和 session 删除正确\n52: \n53: ---\n54: \n55: ## Phase 2: AgentRuntimeClient 补充测试\n56: \n57: - [ ] **T2.1** 测试环境变量解析\n58:   - 测试 `router_url` 从 `AGENTCUBE_ROUTER_URL` 读取\n59:   - 测试环境变量缺失时抛出 `ValueError`\n60:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n61:   - Verify: 环境变量正确解析\n62: \n63: - [ ] **T2.2** 测试 `__init__` 参数\n64:   - 测试 `timeout` 默认值为 120\n65:   - 测试 `connect_timeout` 默认值为 5.0\n66:   - 测试 `namespace` 默认值为 \"default\"\n67:   - 测试提供 `session_id` 时不调用 `bootstrap`\n68:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n69:   - Verify: 默认值和初始化逻辑正确\n70: \n71: - [ ] **T2.3** 测试上下文管理器\n72:   - 测试 `__enter__` 返回 `self`\n73:   - 测试 `__exit__` 调用 `close()`\n74:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n75:   - Verify: 上下文管理器行为正确\n76: \n77: - [ ] **T2.4** 测试 `invoke()` 方法\n78:   - 测试未初始化 `session_id` 时抛出 `ValueError`\n79:   - 测试自定义 `timeout` 传递给 data plane\n80:   - 测试正常调用返回 parsed JSON\n81:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n82:   - Verify: 参数传递和错误处理正确\n83: \n84: - [ ] **T2.5** 测试 `bootstrap_session_id` 失败场景\n85:   - 测试缺少 session header 时抛出 `ValueError`\n86:   - 测试 HTTP 错误处理\n87:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n88:   - Verify: bootstrap 错误处理正确\n89: \n90: - [ ] **T2.6** 测试 `close()` 方法\n91:   - 测试调用 `dp_client.close()`\n92:   - File: `sdk-python/tests/unit/test_agent_runtime.py`\n93:   - Verify: 资源清理正确\n94: \n95: ---\n96: \n97: ## Phase 3: ControlPlaneClient 补充测试\n98: \n99: - [ ] **T3.1** 测试环境变量解析\n100:   - 测试 `workload_manager_url` 从 `AGENTCUBE_WORKLOAD_MANAGER_UR