{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894843101,"sessionID":"ses_2846bbb18ffeBd5AO4CTt4ZY4U","part":{"id":"prt_d7b94c9e4001PUOk6aKSadzNTO","messageID":"msg_d7b94bbec001gZA3x7GTgOcotf","sessionID":"ses_2846bbb18ffeBd5AO4CTt4ZY4U","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_2b3ef4005b2346e694d23dc3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-043/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-043/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-043: 架构设计文档与 API 文档\n2: \n3: ## 1. Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 AgentCube 项目创建完整的架构设计文档和 API 文档，建立统一的技术文档体系，服务于开发者、运维人员和技术决策者。\n6: \n7: 本提案针对 AR-043 需求，建立以下核心能力：\n8: \n9: 1. **架构设计文档** - 系统化记录系统架构、设计决策、组件交互\n10: 2. **API 参考文档** - 提供完整的 API 接口说明和使用示例\n11: 3. **设计规范沉淀** - 将分散的设计文档整合到统一框架\n12: 4. **文档可维护性** - 建立文档更新机制，确保与代码同步\n13: 5. **开发者体验提升** - 降低新成员理解成本，加速开发效率\n14: \n15: 本文档将作为 AR-042 文档站的核心内容来源，与 Docusaurus 文档站形成互补。\n16: \n17: ## 2. Scope\n18: \n19: **Module:** `docs/`  \n20: **Language:** Markdown  \n21: **Size:** M\n22: \n23: ### 2.1 In Scope\n24: \n25: | 文档类别 | 文件 | 优先级 | 内容类型 | 状态 |\n26: |----------|------|--------|----------|------|\n27: | **架构设计文档** | | | | |\n28: | 架构概览 | `docs/architecture/overview.md` | P0 | Markdown + 架构图 | 需要创建 |\n29: | 核心组件设计 | `docs/architecture/components.md` | P0 | Markdown + 序列图 | 需要创建 |\n30: | 数据流设计 | `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` | P0 | Markdown + 流程图 | 需要创建 |\n31: | 部署架构 | `docs/architecture/deployment.md` | P1 | Markdown + 部署图 | 需要创建 |\n32: | 安全架构 | `docs/architecture/security.md` | P1 | Markdown | 需要创建 |\n33: | **API 文档** | | | | |\n34: | Router API | `docs/api/router.md` | P0 | Markdown + 示例 | 需要创建 |\n35: | Workload Manager API | `docs/api/workload-manager.md` | P0 | Markdown + 示例 | 需要创建 |\n36: | Store API | `docs/api/store.md` | P0 | Markdown + 示例 | 需要创建 |\n37: | Sandbox Manager API | `docs/api/sandbox-manager.md` | P1 | Markdown + 示例 | 需要创建 |\n38: | PicoD API | `docs/api/picod.md` | P1 | Markdown + 示例 | 需要创建 |\n39: | **设计规范** | | | | |\n40: | 代码设计规范 | `docs/design/coding-standards.md` | P2 | Markdown | 需要创建 |\n41: | 命名规范 | `docs/design/naming-conventions.md` | P2 | Markdown | 需要创建 |\n42: | 错误处理规范 | `docs/design/error-handling.md` | P2 | Markdown | 需要创建 |\n43: \n44: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n45: \n46: - 用户指南和操作手册（由运维文档负责）\n47: - SDK 使用文档（由 SDK 文档负责）\n48: - 快速入门教程（由 quickstart 负责）\n49: - 博客和公告（由 Docusaurus Blog 负责）\n50: - API 交互式测试工具（由 Swagger/OpenAPI 负责）\n51: \n52: ## 3. Current State Analysis\n53: \n54: ### 3.1 现有文档资产\n55: \n56: 当前项目中的设计和 API 文档分散在多个位置：\n57: \n58: | 文档类型 | 位置 | 格式 | 状态 |\n59: |----------|------|------|------|\n60: | 设计规范 | `design.md` | Markdown | 已有，需更新 |\n61: | 增量规范 | `delta-spec.md`, `delta-spec-ar-021.md` 等 | Markdown | 分散 |\n62: | 部署设计 | `deployment/design.md` | Markdown | 已有 |\n63: | 客户端设计 | `client-go/design.md` | Markdown | 已有 |\n64: | 各模块设计 | `pkg/*/design.md` | Markdown | 部分已有 |\n65: | API 定义 | `pkg/apis/` | Go types | 代码即文档 |\n66: | 提案文档 | `changes/AR-*/proposal.md` | Markdown | 分散 |\n67: \n68: ### 3.2 Gaps Identified\n69: \n70: 1. **架构文档缺失** - 缺少统一的架构概览和组件设计文档\n71: 2. **API 文档不完整** - API 说明分散在代码和提案中，无统一参考\n72: 3. **设计决策未沉淀** - 重要设计决策散落在 AR 提案中，难以追溯\n73: 4. **文档风格不一** - 不同文档采用不同结构和术语\n74: 5. **更新滞后** - 文档与代码实现不同步\n75: 6. **缺少图示** - 架构图、序列图、流程图不足\n76: \n77: ### 3.3 与 AR-042 文档站的关系\n78: \n79: | 维度 | AR-043 (本文档) | AR-042 (Docusaurus) |\n80: |------|-----------------|---------------------|\n81: | 定位 | 技术设计文档 | 用户文档站点 |\n82: | 读者 | 开发者、架构师 | 开发者、运维、用户 |\n83: | 内容 | 架构、API、设计规范 | 使用指南、教程、参考 |\n84: | 格式 | Markdown 文件 | Docusaurus 站点 |\n85: | 更新频率 | 随代码变更 | 随版本发布 |\n86: | 关系 | 内容来源 | 展示平台 |\n87: \n88: ## 4. Proposed Changes\n89: \n90: ### 4.1 目录结构\n91: \n92: ```\n93: docs/\n94: ├── architecture/                    # 架构设计文档\n95: │   ├── overview.md                  # 架构概览\n96: │   ├── components.md                # 核心组件设计\n97: │   ├── data-flow.md                 # 数据流设计\n98: │   ├── deployment.md                # 部署架构\n99: │   └── security.md                  # 安全架构\n100: ├── api/                             # API 文档\n101: │   ├── README.md                    # API 文档索引\n102: │   ├── router.md                    # Router API\n103: │   ├── workload-manager.md          # Workload Manager API\n104: │   ├── store.md                     # Store API\n105: │   ├── sandbox-manager.md           # Sandbox Manager API\n106: │   └── picod.md                     # PicoD API\n107: ├── design/                          # 设计规范\n108: │   ├── coding-standards.md          # 代码设计规范\n109: │   ├── naming-conventions.md        # 命名规范\n110: │   └── error-handling.md            # 错误处理规范\n111: └── README.md                        # 文档说明\n112: ```\n113: \n114: ### 4.2 架构设计文档\n115: \n116: #### 4.2.1 架构概览 (`docs/architecture/overview.md`)\n117: \n118: ```markdown\n119: # AgentCube 架构概览\n120: \n121: ## 系统愿景\n122: \n123: AgentCube 是一个 Kubernetes-native 的沙箱编排平台，用于 AI Agent 的隔离执行和会话管理。\n124: \n125: ## 架构分层\n126: \n127: ```\n128: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n129: │              Client Layer               │\n130: │  (Python SDK, CLI, REST API Clients)    │\n131: └─────────────────┬───────────────────────┘\n132:                   │\n133:                   ▼\n134: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n135: │             API Gateway                 │\n136: │            (Router + LB)                │\n137: └─────────────────┬───────────────────────┘\n138:                   │\n139:         ┌─────────┴─────────┐\n140:         │                   │\n141:         ▼                   ▼\n142: ┌──────────────┐    ┌──────────────┐\n143: │   Session    │    │   Workload   │\n144: │   Routing    │    │   Manager    │\n145: └──────┬───────┘    └──────┬───────┘\n146:        │                   │\n147:        └─────────┬─────────┘\n148:                  │\n149:                  ▼\n150: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n151: │          Sandbox Orchestration          │\n152: │    (Sandbox Pods + PicoD + Runtime)     │\n153: └─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n154:                  │\n155:                  ▼\n156: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n157: │            State Storage                │\n158: │         (Redis/Valkey Cluster)          │\n159: └─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n160: ```\n161: \n162: ## 核心组件\n163: \n164: | 组件 | 职责 | 技术栈 |\n165: |------|------|--------|\n166: | Router | 会话路由、负载均衡 | Go, Kubernetes Informer |\n167: | Workload Manager | 工作负载编排、生命周期管理 | Go, Kubernetes Controller |\n168: | Sandbox Manager | 沙箱创建、更新、删除 | Go, Kubernetes Client |\n169: | Store | 会话状态存储 | Redis/Valkey, Go |\n170: | PicoD | 沙箱内命令执行 | Go, HTTP Server |\n171: \n172: ## 关键设计决策\n173: \n174: 1. **Kubernetes-native** - 基于 CRD 和 Controller 模式\n175: 2. **会话亲和性** - 基于会话 ID 的路由策略\n176: 3. **温池优化** - 预创建沙箱加速启动\n177: 4. **隔离执行** - 每个 Agent 独立沙箱环境\n178: ```\n179: \n180: #### 4.2.2 核心组件设计 (`docs/architecture/components.md`)\n181: \n182: ```markdown\n183: # 核心组件设计\n184: \n185: ## Router\n186: \n187: ### 职责\n188: - 接收客户端请求\n189: - 解析会话 ID\n190: - 路由到对应后端 Agent\n191: - 维护会话 - 后端映射关系\n192: \n193: ### 架构\n194: \n195: ```\n196: ┌─────────────┐\n197: │   Client    │\n198: └──────┬──────┘\n199:        │\n200:        ▼\n201: ┌─────────────┐\n202: │   Router    │──────► Redis (Session Store)\n203: └──────┬──────┘\n204:        │\n205:        ▼\n206: ┌─────────────┐\n207: │Agent Pod 1  │\n208: └─────────────┘\n209: ```\n210: \n211: ### 关键接口\n212: \n213: ```go\n214: type Router interface {\n215:     // Route routes a request to the appropriate backend\n216:     Route(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*Backend, error)\n217:     \n218:     // RegisterBackend registers a backend for a session\n219:     RegisterBackend(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, backend *Backend) error\n220:     \n221:     // UnregisterBackend removes a backend registration\n222:     UnregisterBackend(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n223: }\n224: ```\n225: \n226: ## Workload Manager\n227: \n228: ### 职责\n229: - 监听 CodeInterpreter CR\n230: - 创建和管理 Sandbox Pod\n231: - 处理扩缩容\n232: - 管理温池\n233: \n234: ### 架构\n235: \n236: ```\n237: ┌──────────────────┐\n238: │ CodeInterpreter  │\n239: │       CR         │\n240: └────────┬─────────┘\n241:          │ Watch\n242:          ▼\n243: ┌──────────────────┐\n244: │   Workload       │\n245: │   Manager        │\n246: └────────┬─────────┘\n247:          │ Create/Update/Delete\n248:          ▼\n249: ┌──────────────────┐\n250: │   Sandbox Pod    │\n251: └──────────────────┘\n252: ```\n253: \n254: ## Store\n255: \n256: ### 职责\n257: - 存储会话状态\n258: - 存储会话 - 后端映射\n259: - 提供 TTL 过期机制\n260: \n261: ### 架构\n262: \n263: ```\n264: ┌─────────────┐\n265: │   Router    │\n266: └──────┬──────┘\n267:        │\n268:        ▼\n269: ┌─────────────┐\n270: │    Store    │──────► Redis Cluster\n271: └─────────────┘\n272: ```\n273: ```\n274: \n275: #### 4.2.3 数据流设计 (`docs/architecture/data-flow.md`)\n276: \n277: ```markdown\n278: # 数据流设计\n279: \n280: ## 请求处理流程\n281: \n282: ### 1. 会话创建流程\n283: \n284: ```\n285: Client ──► Router ──► Store ──► Workload Manager ──► Sandbox Pod\n286:    │          │           │            │                  │\n287:    │          │           │            │                  │\n288:    │          │           │            │◄── Create CR ────┘\n289:    │          │           │            │\n290:    │          │           │◄── Set Session ──┘\n291:    │          │           │\n292:    │          │◄── Return Backend URL\n293:    │          │\n294:    │◄── Return Response\n295:    │\n296: ```\n297: \n298: ### 2. 请求路由流程\n299: \n300: ```\n301: Client ──► Router ──► Store ──► Get Backend URL ──► Agent Pod\n302:    │          │           │\n303:    │          │           │\n304:    │          │◄── Lookup Session\n305:    │          │\n306:    │◄── Forward Response\n307:    │\n308: ```\n309: \n310: ### 3. 会话过期流程\n311: \n312: ```\n313: Store ──► TTL Expires ──► Redis Key Deleted\n314:    │\n315:    │ Notify (Keyspace Notification)\n316:    ▼\n317: Workload Manager ──► Delete Sandbox Pod\n318: ```\n319: \n320: ## 状态变更流程\n321: \n322: ### Sandbox 生命周期\n323: \n324: ```\n325: Pending ──► Creating ──► Running ──► Idle ──► Terminating ──► Terminated\n326:               │            │         │          │\n327:               │            │         │          │\n328:               └────────────┴─────────┴──────────┘\n329:                        Error Path\n330: ```\n331: ```\n332: \n333: #### 4.2.4 部署架构 (`docs/architecture/deployment.md`)\n334: \n335: ```markdown\n336: # 部署架构\n337: \n338: ## 部署模式\n339: \n340: ### 开发环境 (Kind)\n341: \n342: ```\n343: ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n344: │         Kind Cluster                │\n345: │  ┌───────────────────────────────┐  │\n346: │  │  agentcube-system Namespace   │  │\n347: │  │  - Router Deployment          │  │\n348: │  │  - Workload Manager           │  │\n349: │  │  - Redis StatefulSet          │  │\n350: │  └───────────────────────────────┘  │\n351: │  ┌───────────────────────────────┐  │\n352: │  │  default Namespace            │  │\n353: │  │  - Sandbox Pods               │  │\n354: │  └───────────────────────────────┘  │\n355: └─────────────────────────────────────┘\n356: ```\n357: \n358: ### 生产环境 (多集群)\n359: \n360: ```\n361: ┌──────────────────┐\n362: │   Load Balancer  │\n363: └────────┬─────────┘\n364:          │\n365:     ┌────┴────┐\n366:     ▼         ▼\n367: ┌───────┐ ┌───────┐\n368: │Cluster│ │Cluster│\n369: │  A    │ │  B    │\n370: └───────┘ └───────┘\n371: ```\n372: \n373: ## 资源配置\n374: \n375: | 组件 | CPU Request | Memory Request | CPU Limit | Memory Limit |\n376: |------|-------------|----------------|-----------|--------------|\n377: | Router | 100m | 128Mi | 500m | 512Mi |\n378: | Workload Manager | 200m | 256Mi | 1000m | 1Gi |\n379: | Redis | 500m | 1Gi | 2000m | 4Gi |\n380: | Sandbox Pod | 100m | 64Mi | 500m | 128Mi |\n381: ```\n382: \n383: #### 4.2.5 安全架构 (`docs/architecture/security.md`)\n384: \n385: ```markdown\n386: # 安全架构\n387: \n388: ## 安全边界\n389: \n390: ```\n391: ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n392: │         External Network            │\n393: └──────────────┬──────────────────────┘\n394:                │\n395:                ▼\n396: ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n397: │         API Gateway (Router)        │\n398: │         - JWT Authentication        │\n399: │         - Rate Limiting             │\n400: └──────────────┬──────────────────────┘\n401:                │\n402:                ▼\n403: ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n404: │         Internal Network            │\n405: │         - Network Policies          │\n406: │         - Service Mesh (optional)   │\n407: └──────────────┬──────────────────────┘\n408:                │\n409:                ▼\n410: ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n411: │         Sandbox Pod                 │\n412: │         - Non-root User             │\n413: │         - Read-only Root FS         │\n414: │         - Dropped Capabilities      │\n415: │         - Resource Quotas           │\n416: └─────────────────────────────────────┘\n417: ```\n418: \n419: ## 认证授权\n420: \n421: | 层级 | 机制 | 说明 |\n422: |------|------|------|\n423: | API Gateway | JWT Token | 客户端认证 |\n424: | Service-to-Service | mTLS | 服务间认证 |\n425: | PicoD | RSA Key Pair | 沙箱内命令执行认证 |\n426: | Kubernetes | RBAC | 集群资源访问控制 |\n427: \n428: ## 沙箱安全\n429: \n430: - 运行在非 root 用户\n431: - 只读根文件系统\n432: - 丢弃所有 capabilities\n433: - 限制系统调用\n434: - 网络命名空间隔离\n435: - 资源配额限制\n436: ```\n437: \n438: ### 4.3 API 文档\n439: \n440: #### 4.3.1 Router API (`docs/api/router.md`)\n441: \n442: ```markdown\n443: # Router API\n444: \n445: ## Overview\n446: \n447: Router 提供请求路由和会话管理服务。\n448: \n449: ## Endpoints\n450: \n451: ### POST /api/v1/sessions\n452: \n453: 创建新会话。\n454: \n455: **Request**\n456: \n457: ```json\n458: {\n459:   \"agentRuntime\": \"echo-agent\",\n460:   \"namespace\": \"default\",\n461:   \"ttl\": \"5m\"\n462: }\n463: ```\n464: \n465: **Response**\n466: \n467: ```json\n468: {\n469:   \"sessionID\": \"sess_abc123\",\n470:   \"backendURL\": \"http://echo-agent-svc:8080\",\n471:   \"expiresAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:05:00Z\"\n472: }\n473: ```\n474: \n475: ### GET /api/v1/sessions/:sessionID\n476: \n477: 获取会话信息。\n478: \n479: **Response**\n480: \n481: ```json\n482: {\n483:   \"sessionID\": \"sess_abc123\",\n484:   \"backendURL\": \"http://echo-agent-svc:8080\",\n485:   \"status\": \"active\",\n486:   \"expiresAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:05:00Z\"\n487: }\n488: ```\n489: \n490: ### DELETE /api/v1/sessions/:sessionID\n491: \n492: 删除会话。\n493: \n494: **Response**\n495: \n496: ```json\n497: {\n498:   \"status\": \"deleted\"\n499: }\n500: ```\n501: \n502: ## Client Example\n503: \n504: ### Python SDK\n505: \n506: ```python\n507: from agentcube import Client\n508: \n509: client = Client(base_url=\"http://router:8080\")\n510: \n511: # Create session\n512: session = client.create_session(\n513:     agent_runtime=\"echo-agent\",\n514:     namespace=\"default\",\n515:     ttl=\"5m\"\n516: )\n517: \n518: print(f\"Session ID: {session.id}\")\n519: print(f\"Backend URL: {session.backend_url}\")\n520: \n521: # Get session info\n522: session = client.get_session(session.id)\n523: \n524: # Delete session\n525: client.delete_session(session.id)\n526: ```\n527: ```\n528: \n529: #### 4.3.2 Workload Manager API (`docs/api/workload-manager.md`)\n530: \n531: ```markdown\n532: # Workload Manager API\n533: \n534: ## Overview\n535: \n536: Workload Manager 提供工作负载编排和管理服务。\n537: \n538: ## Endpoints\n539: \n540: ### POST /api/v1/workloads\n541: \n542: 创建工作负载。\n543: \n544: **Request**\n545: \n546: ```json\n547: {\n548:   \"name\": \"echo-agent-1\",\n549:   \"namespace\": \"default\",\n550:   \"agentRuntime\": \"echo-agent\",\n551:   \"replicas\": 1,\n552:   \"resources\": {\n553:     \"requests\": {\n554:       \"cpu\": \"100m\",\n555:       \"memory\": \"64Mi\"\n556:     },\n557:     \"limits\": {\n558:       \"cpu\": \"500m\",\n559:       \"memory\": \"128Mi\"\n560:     }\n561:   }\n562: }\n563: ```\n564: \n565: **Response**\n566: \n567: ```json\n568: {\n569:   \"name\": \"echo-agent-1\",\n570:   \"status\": \"creating\",\n571:   \"pods\": []\n572: }\n573: ```\n574: \n575: ### GET /api/v1/workloads/:name\n576: \n577: 获取工作负载状态。\n578: \n579: **Response**\n580: \n581: ```json\n582: {\n583:   \"name\": \"echo-agent-1\",\n584:   \"status\": \"running\",\n585:   \"replicas\": {\n586:     \"desired\": 1,\n587:     \"ready\": 1\n588:   },\n589:   \"pods\": [\n590:     {\n591:       \"name\": \"echo-agent-1-abc123\",\n592:       \"phase\": \"Running\",\n593:       \"ip\": \"10.244.0.5\"\n594:     }\n595:   ]\n596: }\n597: ```\n598: \n599: ### PATCH /api/v1/workloads/:name/scale\n600: \n601: 扩缩容工作负载。\n602: \n603: **Request**\n604: \n605: ```json\n606: {\n607:   \"replicas\": 3\n608: }\n609: ```\n610: \n611: ### DELETE /api/v1/workloads/:name\n612: \n613: 删除工作负载。\n614: ```\n615: \n616: #### 4.3.3 Store API (`docs/api/store.md`)\n617: \n618: ```markdown\n619: # Store API\n620: \n621: ## Overview\n622: \n623: Store 提供会话状态存储服务。\n624: \n625: ## Interface\n626: \n627: ```go\n628: type Store interface {\n629:     // Set sets a key-value pair with optional TTL\n630:     Set(ctx context.Context, key string, value []byte, ttl time.Duration) error\n631:     \n632:     // Get gets a value by key\n633:     Get(ctx context.Context, key string) ([]byte, error)\n634:     \n635:     // Delete deletes a key\n636:     Delete(ctx context.Context, key string) error\n637:     \n638:     // Exists checks if a key exists\n639:     Exists(ctx context.Context, key string) (bool, error)\n640:     \n641:     // Watch watches for key changes\n642:     Watch(ctx context.Context, key string) (<-chan Event, error)\n643: }\n644: \n645: type Event struct {\n646:     Type  EventType\n647:     Key   string\n648:     Value []byte\n649: }\n650: \n651: type EventType string\n652: \n653: const (\n654:     EventSet    EventType = \"set\"\n655:     EventDelete EventType = \"delete\"\n656: )\n657: ```\n658: \n659: ## Usage Example\n660: \n661: ```go\n662: import \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store\"\n663: \n664: // Create store\n665: s := store.NewRedisStore(redisClient)\n666: \n667: // Set with TTL\n668: err := s.Set(ctx, \"session:abc123\", []byte(\"backend-url\"), 5*time.Minute)\n669: \n670: // Get\n671: value, err := s.Get(ctx, \"session:abc123\")\n672: \n673: // Watch\n674: events, err := s.Watch(ctx, \"session:abc123\")\n675: for event := range events {\n676:     fmt.Printf(\"Event: %s %s\\n\", event.Type, event.Key)\n677: }\n678: ```\n679: ```\n680: \n681: #### 4.3.4 Sandbox Manager API (`docs/api/sandbox-manager.md`)\n682: \n683: ```markdown\n684: # Sandbox Manager API\n685: \n686: ## Overview\n687: \n688: Sandbox Manager 提供沙箱生命周期管理服务。\n689: \n690: ## Interface\n691: \n692: ```go\n693: type SandboxManager interface {\n694:     // Create creates a new sandbox\n695:     Create(ctx context.Context, sandbox *SandboxInfo) error\n696:     \n697:     // Update updates an existing sandbox\n698:     Update(ctx context.Context, sandbox *SandboxInfo) error\n699:     \n700:     // Delete deletes a sandbox\n701:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name, namespace string) error\n702:     \n703:     // Get gets a sandbox by name\n704:     Get(ctx context.Context, name, namespace string) (*SandboxInfo, error)\n705:     \n706:     // List lists sandboxes by selector\n707:     List(ctx context.Context, selector labels.Selector) ([]*SandboxInfo, error)\n708:     \n709:     // WarmPool manages warm pool\n710:     WarmPool() WarmPoolManager\n711: }\n712: \n713: type WarmPoolManager interface {\n714:     // Precreate pre-creates sandboxes\n715:     Precreate(ctx context.Context, spec *SandboxSpec, count int) error\n716:     \n717:     // Acquire acquires a sandbox from warm pool\n718:     Acquire(ctx context.Context) (*SandboxInfo, error)\n719:     \n720:     // Refill refills warm pool\n721:     Refill(ctx context.Context, spec *SandboxSpec) error\n722: }\n723: ```\n724: \n725: ## Usage Example\n726: \n727: ```go\n728: import \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox\"\n729: \n730: // Create manager\n731: mgr := sandbox.NewManager(kubeClient)\n732: \n733: // Create sandbox\n734: sandbox := &sandbox.SandboxInfo{\n735:     Name:      \"echo-agent-1\",\n736:     Namespace: \"default\",\n737:     Spec: sandbox.SandboxSpec{\n738:         Image: \"volcanosh/echo-agent:latest\",\n739:     },\n740: }\n741: err := mgr.Create(ctx, sandbox)\n742: \n743: // Acquire from warm pool\n744: sandbox, err := mgr.WarmPool().Acquire(ctx)\n745: ```\n746: ```\n747: \n748: #### 4.3.5 PicoD API (`docs/api/picod.md`)\n749: \n750: ```markdown\n751: # PicoD API\n752: \n753: ## Overview\n754: \n755: PicoD 是沙箱内的命令执行服务。\n756: \n757: ## Interface\n758: \n759: ```go\n760: type PicoD interface {\n761:     // Run executes a command and waits for completion\n762:     Run(ctx context.Context, cmd *Command) (*CommandResult, error)\n763:     \n764:     // Start starts a command without waiting\n765:     Start(ctx context.Context, cmd *Command) (*Process, error)\n766:     \n767:     // RunWithStreaming executes a command with streaming output\n768:     RunWithStreaming(ctx context.Context, cmd *Command, handler OutputHandler) (*CommandResult, error)\n769: }\n770: \n771: type Command struct {\n772:     Path  string\n773:     Args  []string\n774:     Env   []string\n775:     Dir   string\n776:     Stdin io.Reader\n777: }\n778: \n779: type CommandResult struct {\n780:     ExitCode  int\n781:     Stdout    []byte\n782:     Stderr    []byte\n783:     Duration  time.Duration\n784:     OOMKilled bool\n785:     Timeout   bool\n786: }\n787: ```\n788: \n789: ## Usage Example\n790: \n791: ```go\n792: import \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/picod\"\n793: \n794: // Create PicoD\n795: p := picod.New(\"sandbox-123\",\n796:     picod.WithWorkDir(\"/workspace\"),\n797:     picod.WithLimits(&picod.ResourceLimits{\n798:         Timeout: 30 * time.Second,\n799:         MaxMemory: 128 * 1024 * 1024,\n800:     }),\n801: )\n802: \n803: // Run command\n804: cmd := &picod.Command{\n805:     Path: \"python\",\n806:     Args: []string{\"-c\", \"print('hello')\"},\n807: }\n808: result, err := p.Run(ctx, cmd)\n809: \n810: fmt.Printf(\"Exit code: %d\\n\", result.ExitCode)\n811: fmt.Printf(\"Output: %s\\n\", result.Stdout)\n812: ```\n813: \n814: ## HTTP Endpoints\n815: \n816: PicoD daemon exposes HTTP endpoints:\n817: \n818: ### POST /execute\n819: \n820: Execute a command.\n821: \n822: **Request**\n823: \n824: ```json\n825: {\n826:   \"command\": \"python\",\n827:   \"args\": [\"-c\", \"print('hello')\"],\n828:   \"env\": {\"PYTHONUNBUFFERED\": \"1\"},\n829:   \"timeout\": \"30s\"\n830: }\n831: ```\n832: \n833: **Response**\n834: \n835: ```json\n836: {\n837:   \"exitCode\": 0,\n838:   \"stdout\": \"hello\\n\",\n839:   \"stderr\": \"\",\n840:   \"duration\": \"0.1s\"\n841: }\n842: ```\n843: \n844: ### GET /health\n845: \n846: Health check endpoint.\n847: ```\n848: \n849: ### 4.4 设计规范文档\n850: \n851: #### 4.4.1 代码设计规范 (`docs/design/coding-standards.md`)\n852: \n853: ```markdown\n854: # 代码设计规范\n855: \n856: ## Go 代码规范\n857: \n858: ### 代码格式\n859: \n860: - 使用 `gofmt` 或 `goimports` 格式化代码\n861: - 行宽限制 120 字符\n862: - 使用 tab 缩进\n863: \n864: ### 命名规范\n865: \n866: - 包名小写，无下划线\n867: - 导出的标识符大写首字母\n868: - 私有标识符小写首字母\n869: \n870: ### 错误处理\n871: \n872: - 使用 `errors.Wrap` 添加上下文\n873: - 错误信息小写开头\n874: - 不忽略错误\n875: \n876: ### 测试规范\n877: \n878: - 测试文件 `*_test.go`\n879: - 测试函数 `TestXxx`\n880: - 表格驱动测试优先\n881: ```\n882: \n883: #### 4.4.2 命名规范 (`docs/design/naming-conventions.md`)\n884: \n885: ```markdown\n886: # 命名规范\n887: \n888: ## CRD 命名\n889: \n890: - 复数形式：`agentruntimes`, `codeinterpreters`\n891: - 短名称：`ar`, `ci`\n892: \n893: ## API Group\n894: \n895: - 格式：`<resource>.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n896: - 版本：`v1alpha1`, `v1beta1`, `v1`\n897: \n898: ## 环境变量\n899: \n900: - 前缀：`AGENTCUBE_`\n901: - 大写：`AGENTCUBE_ROUTER_PORT`\n902: ```\n903: \n904: #### 4.4.3 错误处理规范 (`docs/design/error-handling.md`)\n905: \n906: ```markdown\n907: # 错误处理规范\n908: \n909: ## 错误类型\n910: \n911: ```go\n912: type Error struct {\n913:     Code    string\n914:     Message string\n915:     Cause   error\n916: }\n917: ```\n918: \n919: ## 错误码\n920: \n921: | 错误码 | 说明 |\n922: |--------|------|\n923: | `ERR_INVALID_INPUT` | 无效输入 |\n924: | `ERR_NOT_FOUND` | 资源不存在 |\n925: | `ERR_ALREADY_EXISTS` | 资源已存在 |\n926: | `ERR_TIMEOUT` | 超时 |\n927: | `ERR_INTERNAL` | 内部错误 |\n928: \n929: ## 错误处理模式\n930: \n931: ```go\n932: if err != nil {\n933:     return nil, errors.Wrap(err, \"failed to create sandbox\")\n934: }\n935: ```\n936: ```\n937: \n938: ## 5. Impact Analysis\n939: \n940: ### 5.1 依赖\n941: \n942: | 依赖 | 用途 | 版本 |\n943: |------|------|------|\n944: | Markdown | 文档格式 | - |\n945: | Mermaid | 图表绘制 | 10.x |\n946: | Go | API 示例代码 | 1.21+ |\n947: | Python | SDK 示例代码 | 3.8+ |\n948: \n949: ### 5.2 受影响组件\n950: \n951: 1. **现有文档** - 需要整合和更新到新的目录结构\n952: 2. **开发流程** - 新增文档审查环节\n953: 3. **代码审查** - 需要确保代码与文档一致\n954: \n955: ### 5.3 向后兼容性\n956: \n957: - 现有文档保持可用\n958: - 老链接需要重定向配置\n959: - 建议设置文档版本标记\n960: \n961: ### 5.4 风险评估\n962: \n963: | 风险 | 可能性 | 影响 | 缓解措施 |\n964: |------|--------|------|----------|\n965: | 文档与代码不同步 | 高 | 中 | 文档审查 + CI 检查 |\n966: | 文档维护成本高 | 中 | 中 | 明确责任人 + 自动化 |\n967: | 图示绘制耗时 | 中 | 低 | 使用 Mermaid 代码绘图 |\n968: | API 变更频繁 | 高 | 低 | 从代码生成 API 文档 |\n969: \n970: ## 6. Alternatives Considered\n971: \n972: ### 6.1 方案 A: 使用 AsciiDoc (不采用)\n973: \n974: **描述**: 使用 AsciiDoc 格式替代 Markdown\n975: \n976: **优点**:\n977: - 更丰富的文档功能\n978: - 内置图表支持\n979: - 交叉引用更强大\n980: \n981: **缺点**:\n982: - 学习曲线陡峭\n983: - GitHub 渲染支持差\n984: - 工具链复杂\n985: \n986: **不采用原因**: Markdown 生态更好，团队熟悉\n987: \n988: ### 6.2 方案 B: 使用 Swagger/OpenAPI (部分采用)\n989: \n990: **描述**: 使用 OpenAPI 规范定义 API\n991: \n992: **优点**:\n993: - 标准化 API 描述\n994: - 可生成客户端代码\n995: - 可交互式测试\n996: \n997: **缺点**:\n998: - 学习成本\n999: - 维护成本高\n1000: - 不适合架构文档\n1001: \n1002: **决策**: 将 API 文档与 OpenAPI 结合，手动维护核心文档\n1003: \n1004: ### 6.3 方案 C: 使用代码生成文档 (部分采用)\n1005: \n1006: **描述**: 从代码注释生成文档 (如 godoc)\n1007: \n1008: **优点**:\n1009: - 文档与代码同步\n1010: - 减少维护成本\n1011: - 自动更新\n1012: \n1013: **缺点**:\n1014: - 缺少架构视角\n1015: - 无法表达设计决策\n1016: - 示例有限\n1017: \n1018: **决策**: 代码注释用于 API 参考，手动编写架构文档\n1019: \n1020: ### 6.4 方案 D: 使用 Wiki (不采用)\n1021: \n1022: **描述**: 使用 GitHub Wiki 或 Confluence\n1023: \n1024: **优点**:\n1025: - 易于编辑\n1026: - 协作方便\n1027: - 版本历史\n1028: \n1029: **缺点**:\n1030: - 难以版本控制\n1031: - 难以审查\n1032: - 导出困难\n1033: \n1034: **不采用原因**: 文档即代码，使用 Git 管理\n1035: \n1036: ## 7. Implementation Plan\n1037: \n1038: ### Phase 1: 架构文档创建 (6h)\n1039: ```\n1040: - [ ] 创建 docs/architecture/ 目录\n1041: - [ ] 编写 overview.md\n1042: - [ ] 编写 components.md\n1043: - [ ] 编写 data-flow.md\n1044: - [ ] 编写 deployment.md\n1045: - [ ] 编写 security.md\n1046: ```\n1047: \n1048: ### Phase 2: API 文档创建 (8h)\n1049: ```\n1050: - [ ] 创建 docs/api/ 目录\n1051: - [ ] 编写 router.md\n1052: - [ ] 编写 workload-manager.md\n1053: - [ ] 编写 store.md\n1054: - [ ] 编写 sandbox-manager.md\n1055: - [ ] 编写 picod.md\n1056: ```\n1057: \n1058: ### Phase 3: 设计规范创建 (4h)\n1059: ```\n1060: - [ ] 创建 docs/design/ 目录\n1061: - [ ] 编写 coding-standards.md\n1062: - [ ] 编写 naming-conventions.md\n1063: - [ ] 编写 error-handling.md\n1064: ```\n1065: \n1066: ### Phase 4: 图示完善 (4h)\n1067: ```\n1068: - [ ] 补充架构图\n1069: - [ ] 补充序列图\n1070: - [ ] 补充流程图\n1071: - [ ] 使用 Mermaid 优化图示\n1072: ```\n1073: \n1074: ### Phase 5: 审查和更新 (2h)\n1075: ```\n1076: - [ ] 代码审查确认 API 准确性\n1077: - [ ] 架构师审查架构文档\n1078: - [ ] 更新现有 design.md\n1079: - [ ] 清理重复文档\n1080: ```\n1081: \n1082: **总预估时间**: 24 小时\n1083: \n1084: ## 8. Acceptance Criteria\n1085: \n1086: - [ ] 所有架构文档创建完成\n1087: - [ ] 所有 API 文档创建完成\n1088: - [ ] 所有设计规范创建完成\n1089: - [ ] 文档包含必要的图示 (架构图、序列图、流程图)\n1090: - [ ] API 文档包含使用示例\n1091: - [ ] 文档通过审查\n1092: - [ ] 文档与代码一致\n1093: - [ ] 文档格式统一\n1094: - [ ] 文档链接正确\n1095: - [ ] 文档更新到 AR-042 文档站\n1096: \n1097: ## 9. Success Criteria\n1098: \n1099: 1. ✅ 架构文档完整描述系统设计\n1100: 2. ✅ API 文档准确反映接口定义\n1101: 3. ✅ 新成员可以通过文档理解系统\n1102: 4. ✅ 开发者可以参考文档编写代码\n1103: 5. ✅ 文档与代码保持同步\n1104: 6. ✅ 文档可以集成到 AR-042 文档站\n1105: 7. ✅ 设计决策可追溯\n1106: \n1107: ## 10. Dependencies\n1108: \n1109: - AR-042: Docusaurus 文档站框架\n1110: - 现有 AR 提案文档\n1111: - 代码实现 (pkg/, cmd/)\n1112: \n1113: ## 11. References\n1114: \n1115: - [project.md](../../project.md) - 项目说明\n1116: - [design.md](../../design.md) - 设计规范\n1117: - `changes/AR-*/proposal.md` - 架构需求文档\n1118: - `pkg/*/design.md` - 模块设计文档\n1119: - [Mermaid 语法](https://mermaid.js.org/) - 图表绘制\n\n(End of file - total 1119 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-043: 架构设计文档与 API 文档\n\n## 1. Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube 项目创建完整的架构设计文档和 API 文档，建立统一的技术文档体系，服务于开发者、运维人员和技术决策者。\n\n本提案针对 AR-043 需求，建立以下核心能力：\n\n1. **架构设计文档** - 系统化记录系统架构、设计决策、组件交互\n2. **API 参考文档** - 提供完整的 API 接口说明和使用示例\n3. **设计规范沉淀** - 将分散的设计文档整合到统一框架\n4. **文档可维护性** - 建立文档更新机制，确保与代码同步\n5. **开发者体验提升** - 降低新成员理解成本，加速开发效率\n\n本文档将作为 AR-042 文档站的核心内容来源，与 Docusaurus 文档站形成互补。\n\n## 2. Scope\n\n**Module:** `docs/`  \n**Language:** Markdown  ","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-043/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775894843087,"end":1775894843098}}}}
